Money Stuff =0A There are two basic ways to use artificial intelligence to =
predict stock =0Aprices: You build a deep learning model to predict stock p=
rices: Yo =0A=0A=0A <> =0A =0A<https://sli.bloomberg.com/click=3Fs=3D825881=
&stpe=3Ddefault&li=3D12737188&m=3D21d6dea82d6b16615cf44233be620525&p=3D0226=
2025>=0A=0A=0A=0ALLM forecasters=0A=0AThere are two basic ways to use artif=
icial intelligence to predict stock =0Aprices:=0A=0A * You build a deep lea=
rning model to predict stock prices: You set up a deep =0Aneural net, you f=
eed it tons of historical data about stocks, and you train it =0Ato figure =
out how that data predicts stock price returns. Then you run the =0Amodel o=
